695
00:59:32,681 --> 00:59:36,288
She might even bring up her pain first.

696
00:59:36,835 --> 00:59:39,876
She might try to use her pain
as a joke to laugh.

697
00:59:41,897 --> 00:59:42,846
But...

698
00:59:45,267 --> 00:59:47,735
...they're all fake.

699
00:59:51,442 --> 00:59:52,725
I was like that.

700
00:59:53,727 --> 00:59:55,082
When my mom...

701
00:59:55,537 --> 00:59:57,539
